      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"letting go\" thing you said... it sounds almost like peace. Because honestly, the effort of just existing right now is so exhausting. Every minute feels like I'm dragging myself through lead. It feels like the only way to actually stop the hurting is to just... stop everything. Like, why am I even fighting to keep a life that feels this broken?",
